snippet.title: this game lets you talk to AI with your voice (and then ABDUCT THEM)
snippet.description:
Play for this game FOR FREE: https://playsnatched.com/

Join our DISCORD: https://discord.gg/p3AYtZYe9D

I built a game demo where you're an alien who abducts humans. 

The catch is the humans are AI and you must use your voice to convince them to come back to your ship.

Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7hOyMUQe2gY
